{
  "name": "Graphic",
  "summary": "<p><strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PageSetup/PageSetup .htm#PageSetup.PageSetup\">PageSetup</a></strong> 对象有若干个属性返回 <strong>Graphic</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PageSetup/PageSetup .htm#PageSetup.CenterFooterPicture\">CenterFooterPicture</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PageSetup/PageSetup .htm#PageSetup.CenterHeaderPicture\">CenterHeaderPicture</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PageSetup/PageSetup .htm#PageSetup.LeftFooterPicture\">LeftFooterPicture</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PageSetup/PageSetup .htm#PageSetup.LeftHeaderPicture\">LeftHeaderPicture</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PageSetup/PageSetup .htm#PageSetup.RightFooterPicture\">RightFooterPicture</a></strong> 或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PageSetup/PageSetup .htm#PageSetup.RightHeaderPicture\">RightHeaderPicture</a></strong> 属性可返回一个 <strong>Graphic</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>要求“&amp;G”为 <strong>LeftFooter</strong> 字符串的一部分，以便在左页脚显示图像。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 C:\\Pictures\\Sample.jpg 添加到页脚的左边。本示例假定名为“Sample.jpg”的文件位于 C:\\Pictures\\ 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FileName</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C:\\\\Pictures\\\\Sample.jpg&quot;</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">275.25</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">463.5</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.36</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> = msoPictureGrayscale\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Contrast</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.39</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropBottom</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">14.4</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropLeft</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">28.8</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropRight</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">14.4</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">21.6</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Enable the image to show up in the left footer.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooter</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&amp;G&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中右页脚图片的颜色转换类型是否为灰度转换。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">msoPictureGrayscale</span> == msoPictureGrayscale)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>包括应用于页眉和页脚的图片对象的属性。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Brightness",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定图片或 OLE 对象的亮度。该属性的值必须是 0.0（最暗）到 1.0（最亮）之间的数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 C:\\Pictures\\Sample.jpg 添加到活动工作表右页眉，并将亮度设置为0.3。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightHeaderPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C:\\\\Pictures\\\\Sample.jpg&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightHeader</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&amp;G&quot;</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中右页脚图片的亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorType",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置应用于指定图片或 OLE 对象的颜色转换类型。<strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/MsoPictureColorType 枚举.html\">MsoPictureColorType</a></strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中右页脚图片的颜色转换类型是否为默认颜色转换。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> == msoPictureAutomatic)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中左页脚图片的颜色转换类型设置为黑白转换。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> = msoPictureBlackAndWhite\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoPictureColorType",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Contrast",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定图片或 OLE 对象的对比度。该属性的值必须是 0.0（最低对比度）到 1.0（最高对比度）的数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置第一张工作表中左页脚图片的对比度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Contrast</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.8</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中右页脚图片的对比度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Contrast</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "CropBottom",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始高度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅高，然后设置 <strong>CropBottom</strong> 属性为 50, 那么从图像的底部切除的将是 100 磅（而不是 50 磅）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的底部所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中左页脚图片底部所裁剪下的磅数设置为20磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此示例可指定从活动工作表中右页脚图片底部裁去的百分比，并裁剪该图片。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the bottom of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span> * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropBottom</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "CropLeft",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始宽度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅宽，然后设置 <strong>CropLeft</strong> 属性为 50, 那么 100 磅（不是 50 磅）将从图像的左边被切除。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的左边所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中左页脚图片左侧所裁剪下的磅数设置为20磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此示例可指定从活动工作表中右页脚图片左侧裁去的百分比，并裁剪该图片。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the left of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span> * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropLeft</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "CropRight",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始宽度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅宽，然后设置 <strong>CropRight</strong> 属性为 50, 那么 100 磅（不是 50 磅）将从图像的右边被切除。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的右边所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中左页脚图片右侧所裁剪下的磅数设置为20磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此示例可指定从活动工作表中右页脚图片右侧裁去的百分比，并裁剪该���片。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the right of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span> * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropRight</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "CropTop",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始高度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅高，然后设置 <strong>CropTop</strong> 属性为 50, 那么 100 磅（不是 50 磅）将从图像的顶部被切除。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的顶部所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中左页脚图片顶部所裁剪下的磅数设置为20磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此示例可指定从活动工作表中右页脚图片顶部裁去的百分比，并裁剪该图片。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the top of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span> * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropTop</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Filename",
      "summary": "<p>如果指定路径中的文件夹不存在，则 <strong>FileName</strong> 属性将产生一个错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置保存指定源对象位置的 URL（Intranet 或网站上）或路径（本地或网络）。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 C:\\Pictures\\Sample.jpg 添加到活动工作表右页眉。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightHeaderPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C:\\\\Pictures\\\\Sample.jpg&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightHeader</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&amp;G&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中右页脚图片的文件名。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Height",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Single</strong> 值，它代表对象的高度（以磅为单位）。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 C:\\ 驱动器中Pictures文件夹中名为“Sample.jpg”的图片添加到活动工作表左页眉部分，并将高度设置为260磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftHeaderPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C:\\\\Pictures\\\\Sample.jpg&quot;</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">260</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftHeader</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&amp;G&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中右页脚图片的高度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "LockAspectRatio",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoTriState</strong> 可为以下 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoCTrue</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoFalse</strong>。调整大小时可以分别更改形状的高度和宽度。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateToggle</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTrue</strong>。指定的形状在调整大小时其原始比例保持不变。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>如果指定的形状在调整大小时其原始比例保持不变，则此属性为 <strong>msoTrue</strong>。如果调整大小时可以分别更改形状的高度和宽度，则此属性为 <strong>msoFalse</strong>。<strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/MsoTriState 枚举.html\">MsoTriState</a></strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中右页脚图片在调整大小时其原始比例是否保持不变。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooterPicture</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LockAspectRatio</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置第一张工作表中左页脚图片在调整大小时可以分别更改图片的高度和宽度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> graphic = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftFooterPicture</span>\n    graphic.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LockAspectRatio</span> = msoFalse\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
